law.history: Repealed 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 14, sec. 491, effective March 19, 1977. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 963d-1, 963e-3, 963e-4.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Civil and criminal cases, where tried when court held at more than one place.
